    <content><![CDATA[<h2 id="终端配置-cmder-babun"><a href="#终端配置-cmder-babun" class="headerlink" title="终端配置 cmder+babun"></a>终端配置 cmder+babun</h2><ul>
<li>给鼠标右键添加访问键，如下图所示，既鼠标右击后按C即可调用。<br><img src="/Notes/2021/02/28/win-notes/access_key.png" width="50%" height="50%" title="鼠标右键添加访问键" alt="鼠标右键添加访问键"><br>在注册表中找到字符串，在其值后面添加(&amp;C)即可，如下图所示。<br><img src="/Notes/2021/02/28/win-notes/reg_value.png" width="50%" height="50%" title="修改注册表值" alt="修改注册表值"><br><a href="https://developer.aliyun.com/article/331226">请参考</a></li>
<li>oh-my-zsh高亮设置，<a href="https://gist.github.com/dogrocker/1efb8fd9427779c827058f873b94df95">请参考</a><br>cmd和cmder不支持socks5代理，只支持http代理，而babun都支持。</li>
<li>cmder加载PATH出错，总是显示<font color="red">此时不应有\cmder\vendor\bin\cexec.cmd…</font>，这是由于读取环境变量格式不一致造成的，应该检查环境变量格式，去除环境变量最后的<code>\</code>和<code>;</code>，<a href="https://blog.csdn.net/qq_39128364/article/details/107675942">请参考</a></li>
</ul>
<h2 id="win-系统配置"><a href="#win-系统配置" class="headerlink" title="win 系统配置"></a>win 系统配置</h2><h3 id="win命令"><a href="#win命令" class="headerlink" title="win命令"></a>win命令</h3><ul>
<li>set 只在本脚本生效</li>
<li>setx 永久生效</li>
<li>/m 系统变量，无/m为用户变量</li>
<li>win+r &amp; <code>powershell -command &quot;&amp;&#123;start-process rundll32.exe sysdm.cpl,EditEnvironmentVariables -verb RunAs&#125;</code> open environment in cmd prompt</li>
</ul>
<h3 id="win输入法配置"><a href="#win输入法配置" class="headerlink" title="win输入法配置"></a>win输入法配置</h3><p>弃用自带微软拼音输入法，用QQ输入法<br>win禁用ctrl-space作为中英文切换键，通过修改注册表完成。<br><figure class="highlight mathematica"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="variable">Windows</span> <span class="variable">Registry</span> <span class="variable">Editor</span> <span class="built_in">Version</span> <span class="number">5.00</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="punctuation">[</span><span class="type">HKEY_CURRENT</span><span class="type">_USER</span>\<span class="built_in">Control</span> <span class="built_in">Panel</span>\<span class="built_in">Input</span> <span class="built_in">Method</span>\<span class="variable">Hot</span> <span class="built_in">Keys</span>\<span class="number">00000010</span><span class="punctuation">]</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&quot;Key Modifiers&quot;</span><span class="operator">=</span><span class="variable">hex</span><span class="operator">:</span><span class="number">00</span><span class="operator">,</span><span class="variable">c0</span><span class="operator">,</span><span class="number">00</span><span class="operator">,</span><span class="number">00</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&quot;Virtual Key&quot;</span><span class="operator">=</span><span class="variable">hex</span><span class="operator">:</span><span class="variable">ff</span><span class="operator">,</span><span class="number">00</span><span class="operator">,</span><span class="number">00</span><span class="operator">,</span><span class="number">00</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="punctuation">[</span><span class="type">HKEY_CURRENT</span><span class="type">_USER</span>\<span class="built_in">Control</span> <span class="built_in">Panel</span>\<span class="built_in">Input</span> <span class="built_in">Method</span>\<span class="variable">Hot</span> <span class="built_in">Keys</span>\<span class="number">00000070</span><span class="punctuation">]</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&quot;Key Modifiers&quot;</span><span class="operator">=</span><span class="variable">hex</span><span class="operator">:</span><span class="number">00</span><span class="operator">,</span><span class="variable">c0</span><span class="operator">,</span><span class="number">00</span><span class="operator">,</span><span class="number">00</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&quot;Virtual Key&quot;</span><span class="operator">=</span><span class="variable">hex</span><span class="operator">:</span><span class="variable">ff</span><span class="operator">,</span><span class="number">00</span><span class="operator">,</span><span class="number">00</span><span class="operator">,</span><span class="number">00</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="punctuation">[</span><span class="type">HKEY_USERS</span>\<span class="operator">.</span><span class="variable">DEFAULT</span>\<span class="built_in">Control</span> <span class="built_in">Panel</span>\<span class="built_in">Input</span> <span class="built_in">Method</span>\<span class="variable">Hot</span> <span class="built_in">Keys</span>\<span class="number">00000010</span><span class="punctuation">]</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&quot;Key Modifiers&quot;</span><span class="operator">=</span><span class="variable">hex</span><span class="operator">:</span><span class="number">02</span><span class="operator">,</span><span class="variable">c0</span><span class="operator">,</span><span class="number">00</span><span class="operator">,</span><span class="number">00</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&quot;Target IME&quot;</span><span class="operator">=</span><span class="variable">hex</span><span class="operator">:</span><span class="number">00</span><span class="operator">,</span><span class="number">00</span><span class="operator">,</span><span class="number">00</span><span class="operator">,</span><span class="number">00</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&quot;Virtual Key&quot;</span><span class="operator">=</span><span class="variable">hex</span><span class="operator">:</span><span class="variable">ff</span><span class="operator">,</span><span class="number">00</span><span class="operator">,</span><span class="number">00</span><span class="operator">,</span><span class="number">00</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="punctuation">[</span><span class="type">HKEY_USERS</span>\<span class="operator">.</span><span class="variable">DEFAULT</span>\<span class="built_in">Control</span> <span class="built_in">Panel</span>\<span class="built_in">Input</span> <span class="built_in">Method</span>\<span class="variable">Hot</span> <span class="built_in">Keys</span>\<span class="number">00000070</span><span class="punctuation">]</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&quot;Key Modifiers&quot;</span><span class="operator">=</span><span class="variable">hex</span><span class="operator">:</span><span class="number">02</span><span class="operator">,</span><span class="variable">c0</span><span class="operator">,</span><span class="number">00</span><span class="operator">,</span><span class="number">00</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&quot;Target IME&quot;</span><span class="operator">=</span><span class="variable">hex</span><span class="operator">:</span><span class="number">00</span><span class="operator">,</span><span class="number">00</span><span class="operator">,</span><span class="number">00</span><span class="operator">,</span><span class="number">00</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&quot;Virtual Key&quot;</span><span class="operator">=</span><span class="variable">hex</span><span class="operator">:</span><span class="variable">ff</span><span class="operator">,</span><span class="number">00</span><span class="operator">,</span><span class="number">00</span><span class="operator">,</span><span class="number">00</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br><a href="https://www.zhihu.com/question/22288432/answer/447721321">请参考</a></p>
<h3 id="win网络设置"><a href="#win网络设置" class="headerlink" title="win网络设置"></a>win网络设置</h3><p>win 开启ping，通过设置防火墙入站规则打开，启动“文件和打印机共享（回显请求-ICMPv4-In）”，并设置作用域为“任何IP”<br>    <img src="/Notes/2021/02/28/win-notes/defender.png" title="打开防火墙" alt="打开防火墙"><br>    <img src="/Notes/2021/02/28/win-notes/defender_domain.png" width="20%" height="20%" title="打开防火墙" alt="打开防火墙"></p>
<p>win windows store内有python，为了避免调用python会打开windows store，需要将自己安装python的路径放在<code>C:\Users\admin\AppData\Local\Microsoft\WindowsApps</code>前面，<a href="https://www.pythonf.cn/read/116736">请参考</a></p>
<p>win 关闭<font color="red">开机自动打开未关闭应用</font>，设置-账户-登录选项-隐私选项 关闭最后一个，<a href="https://www.zhihu.com/question/67295041/answer/468069660">请参考</a></p>
<h2 id="win服务设置"><a href="#win服务设置" class="headerlink" title="win服务设置"></a>win服务设置</h2><ul>
<li>win 路径默认不分区大小写，与Linux不同，可以开启，<a href="https://blog.csdn.net/JerryGou/article/details/84667232">请参考</a>。</li>
<li>win 默认开启ssh client服务，需手动开启ssh server服务，首先需要安装OpenSSH Server，然后启动该服务，<a href="https://blog.csdn.net/joeychiang/article/details/107237490">请参考</a></li>
</ul>
<p>Explorer.exe 是用户与电脑里文件系统、文件互动的软件，类似 Mac OS 里的 Finder，DOS 时代的 <a href="http://command.com，各种UNIX">http://command.com，各种UNIX</a> liker 下的各种 Shell。</p>
<p>添加病毒扫描排除项， win+r, <code>powershell -inputformat none -outputformat none -NonInteractive -Command Add-MpPreference -ExclusionPath $ENV:USERPROFILE\Downloads</code>, ctrl+shift+{Enter}</p>
<p>win 默认以普通用户权限执行任务，即使是用管理员账户登录；当需要提升权限时，系统会给出提示。<a href="https://www.zhihu.com/question/66229405/answer/240508617">请参考</a></p>
<h3 id="win-终端代理设置"><a href="#win-终端代理设置" class="headerlink" title="win 终端代理设置"></a>win 终端代理设置</h3><p><a href="https://ssrvps.org/archives/7544">请参考</a><br>trojian只提供了一个端口，如果command prompt需要代理，则还需要vpn软件，这里使用v2ray+v2rayN，<a href="https://blog.skihome.xyz/posts/trojan/">请参考</a></p>
<ol>
<li>下载v2ray和v2rayN，解压到同一个目录。</li>
<li>添加socks服务，socks默认端口10808，http默认端口10809。</li>
<li>配置代理规则，将需要代理的网址添加到“设置”-“路由设置”-“代理的domain”，<a href="https://github.com/2dust/v2rayN/issues/1366">请参考</a></li>
</ol>
<p>如果IE需要代理，则在“Internet属性”-“连接”-“局域网设置”-“代理服务器”中设置。</p>
<figure class="highlight bat"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">@<span class="built_in">echo</span> off</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">set</span> http_proxy=http://<span class="number">127</span>.<span class="number">0</span>.<span class="number">0</span>.<span class="number">1</span>:<span class="number">10809</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">set</span> https_proxy=http://<span class="number">127</span>.<span class="number">0</span>.<span class="number">0</span>.<span class="number">1</span>:<span class="number">10809</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>取消代理<br><figure class="highlight bat"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">@<span class="built_in">echo</span> off</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">set</span> http_proxy=</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">set</span> https_proxy=</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<h2 id="win-自定义快捷键"><a href="#win-自定义快捷键" class="headerlink" title="win 自定义快捷键"></a>win 自定义快捷键</h2><h3 id="全局快捷键"><a href="#全局快捷键" class="headerlink" title="全局快捷键"></a>全局快捷键</h3><div class="table-container">
