    <url>/Notes/2021/03/17/reinstall-win/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<ul>
<li>C盘下新建LocalProgram目录，作为软件安装目录。</li>
<li>C盘Downloads下新建software、application、library目录，作为文件下载路径。</li>
<li>添加病毒扫描排除项</li>
<li>下载软件QQ输入法，dexpot，emacs，everything，QTTabBar，autohotkey，TrafficMonitor，TranslucentTB，clink，IrfanView，SumatraPDF，tex live    latex，hexo，linux reader，pstools</li>
<li>新建用户lab_user</li>
<li>开启ping功能</li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight bat"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">@<span class="built_in">echo</span> off</span><br><span class="line">runas /user:abc <span class="built_in">cmd</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> /d c:</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">md</span> LocalProgram</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> /d <span class="variable">%userprofile%</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">md</span> user\shell</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">md</span> user\config</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">md</span> user\local</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">md</span> user\shortcut</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> /d <span class="variable">%userprofile%</span>\Downloads</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">md</span> software application library</span><br><span class="line">powershell -inputformat none -outputformat none -NonInteractive -Command Add-MpPreference -ExclusionPath $ENV:USERPROFILE\Downloads</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
